Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得手了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.39,0:00:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糟糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}金蝉脱壳之术
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.75,0:00:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.39,0:01:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已经没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.69,0:01:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.47,0:01:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.65,0:01:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是过去侍奉于此国的大名及领主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.19,0:01:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}从事谍报行动 破坏行动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以及暗杀的人所得到的称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.06,0:01:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这个故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.56,0:01:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}即是讲述作为现代的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为了惩奸除恶而献出青春的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}五位少女们的 爱与勇气的轨迹
Comment: 0,0:02:07.01,0:02:08.65,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,OP校準幀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:14.15,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}消えない鎖 その手で壊して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.95,0:02:33.38,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}惑いに侵されて 心に潜めてた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:36.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}傷だらけの　錆びた刃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:38.46,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}闇雲に翳した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:43.76,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}弱さ認めぬまま 強くはなれないと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:46.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}知った日から　目覚め出した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:48.85,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}確かな熱に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:54.02,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}螺旋の様に 絡まる紅い罠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:03:01.36,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}REALを焼き付けて 彼方へ蹴散ちせ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:07.03,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}遥かな宙に　一瞬の閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:09.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}今 亂れ咲き　影を纏い
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.95,0:03:12.33,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}朧雲に放て
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.86,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}信じる道は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:20.51,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}必ずこの手で切り拓くと誓い立てて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:25.51,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}見えない鎖 撃ち抜けmaze
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.71,0:03:28.29,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}You DON’T need to grieve anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:30.90,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}Who can read the future? Know thyself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:33.34,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}Ready now! Discern truth or false
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.34,0:03:35.30,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}Break your world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:14.15,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}几重枷锁 手中破
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.95,0:02:33.38,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}困惑侵扰 心中隐匿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:36.00,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}斑驳疮痍 刀刃发锈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:38.46,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}却为暗云罩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:43.76,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}不堪羸弱 誓要更强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:46.43,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}自知起 更醒悟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:48.85,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}热忱之切实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:54.02,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}庞若螺旋 赤罠笼络
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:03:01.36,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}铭刻现实 掷向彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:07.03,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}远空迢遥 一瞬閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:09.95,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}绮丽绽放 犹纏暗影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.95,0:03:12.33,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}耀于朧云上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.86,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}所坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:20.51,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}誓以我手 开辟我路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:25.51,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}击穿那道 无形枷锁
