Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又向前迈进了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的力量还仅仅是力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所谓的力量 即是刀与盾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}缺一不可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.57,0:04:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}刀与盾？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}决不能沉溺于力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我一定会不辜负爷爷的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成为一流忍者的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我在努力着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.14,0:04:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}浅草！我回来啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真令人怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这美丽的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:04:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「美丽」么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你住在浅草吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你刚说你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 你听到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}准确来说是无意中听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊！我宿舍在浅草
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然后最近因为点事暂时离开了学校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}结果一回来觉得好怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不经意间就想入神了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}实在不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你真是个有趣的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她是哪里的学生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:30.77,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本船即将抵达浅草
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}国立半藏学院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是一所于1919年立校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全校人数约千人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以大规模重升学而闻名的普通高中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:58.10,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哇 好可爱的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:05:59.37,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}二年级的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:06:00.95,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上去打个招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:04.76,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.14,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.16,0:06:08.97,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可惜了这么个美人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.81,0:06:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}美人…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这也是修行的一环
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但不为人知的是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这所学院还有「表」与「里」两面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.77,0:06:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}斑鸠同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然能巧妙摆脱那几个男生是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被你看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.69,0:06:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但在那之前就该隐藏好气息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且你竟然还从校门悠闲地跑过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久违的返校嘛 一高兴就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们既是本校的学生 又不仅仅是一介学生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}基础都没掌握好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}消沉什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:06:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这可真不像飞鸟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葛城姐…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欢迎回来～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的 让人不能大意啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又不会少块肉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 这样揉揉还能长得更大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才不要！我还想小点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那可真可惜啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才不可惜！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一大早就搞什么呢 云雀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为担心快迟到了…就赶忙跑进来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}结果刹不住车…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 小飞鸟～欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我回来啦 小云雀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}升段考核 合格了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢你～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀你在为别人高兴之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.84,0:07:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还是先担心担心自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没关系啦没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算是别人的事我也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小柳生 你是什么时候来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}隐蔽气息可是忍者的基础
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}说的是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真搞不懂你们谁才是高年级的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是小柳生虽然是一年级的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}段位还在我之上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为小柳生是天才嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全员到齐了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.82,0:08:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雾夜老师 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在…在的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不会…哪说得上…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}卷轴险被夺走 使用了空蝉之术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}并且忍者服装遭到破损
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在商业街上使用了烟雾弹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剩余时间所剩无几
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.13,0:08:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呀 这还真是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}刚好达到了最低合格分数线
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这可不是想考就能考到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别在这种奇怪的地方赞叹啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘛 怎么说也是合格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}期待你日后的精进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天的修行 第一节课是格斗术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:08:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全员换好衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在修行场集合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果雾夜老师不这么神出鬼没的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}倒是位好老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那似乎是他作为忍者的执着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真不愧是雾夜老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得好好学习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对呀～要好好学习哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葛城姐…你又来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}长大咯 长大咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:21.77,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是吧…该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.78,0:09:23.57,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比刚才更大咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:25.57,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别胡闹了 快准备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.63,0:09:27.02,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真不开心…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么了 云雀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为人家…很不擅长格斗技嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.17,0:09:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家准备好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}差不多该过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}首先是空中格斗技
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:09:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}斑鸠 葛城
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}－在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}－在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}内阁特务情报部一科所属
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}特殊机密情报员育成所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}通称为忍者学科
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三年级 斑鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葛城
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真不愧是葛城姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}二年级 飞鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葛城姐 好厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:34.31,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上啊上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一年级 云雀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:35.90,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一年级 柳生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下一组 飞鸟 柳生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:10:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}像这样 这五位少女们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}每天在不为同窗所知之时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}刻苦进行着超乎人智的修行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咱家的全面胜利～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是用剑我可不会输给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘿 死鸭子还嘴硬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才…才不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天的午饭该吃啥好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去外头吃也吃腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.59,0:11:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看这里～～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是外出旅行带回来的礼物～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 粗卷寿司
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.63,0:11:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看起来味道真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天的午饭有着落了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.85,0:11:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟同学 这粗卷寿司是哪里来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其实昨晚我在家里过了一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.39,0:11:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 家里是开寿司店的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好～作为答谢我好好帮你揉揉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦 是粗卷寿司啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:12:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雾夜老师也请
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}半藏大人还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的 托您的福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这粗卷寿司也是爷爷早起做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.51,0:12:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样啊 还是老样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.91,0:12:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那位老先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然飞鸟也回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下午的修行就改为全员在学院外执行任务吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}学院外面？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦！终于等到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最近老在地下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.69,0:12:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又是飞又是跳又是坐禅的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}净是些无聊的修行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}任务是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}整治商店街上的不良少年
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}似乎商店街有不良少年们在闹事 很棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}整治不良少年…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不良少年好口怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}俺来保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.61,0:12:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还以为是要秘密护送VIP啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.23,0:13:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}或者是潜入大使馆偷取秘密情报之类的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.11,0:13:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那种国家级任务是修满毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.37,0:13:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成为出色的忍者们的前辈们的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那也不至于要我们整治不良少年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过这反倒挺难的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}即使面对一般人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也要以忍者之身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神不知鬼不觉地处理好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以才是修行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个…然后不良少年们在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}胡乱瞎转也只是浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}分头寻找目标吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么说也不会在庙里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.59,0:13:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在水上巴士见过的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又见面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是因为修学旅行才到这的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 所以才搭了水上巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}自由活动时间跟朋友走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.15,0:14:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也没有熟悉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们学校还不允许使用手机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是在哪边走散的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像是在什么大道…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.51,0:14:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯…是这附近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}浅草有不少大道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}光知道这点很难确定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还有其他线索吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比起这个 你那边没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}花这么多时间陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.67,0:14:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可你看起来好像有什么急事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没有啦 现在只是校外课程
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}话说 你的学校好像是在这附近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我现在的课是调查周围的名胜古迹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过一下就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}现在闲着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呐 小柳生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么跟着我一起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为我担心你一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}区区的不良少年 云雀一个人也能收拾的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.05,0:15:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}说不定会突然袭击过来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀可以反过来打他们一个落花流水…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这身制服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.00,0:15:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她们是半藏学院的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个大得过分的学校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能不能借点钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.72,0:15:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把大家聚过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍者狼烟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是只有经过训练的忍者才能探知的特殊暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}据说此效果可覆盖周围一公里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.02,0:15:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}基本上都转过了 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对不住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没什么啦 有困难的时候就要互相帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}弁天那边还没去过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你TMD想干架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不可以哦 小柳生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.46,0:16:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那些家伙也是半藏学院的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们做好觉悟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.07,0:16:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}搞…搞什么啊 这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们是拜托来打扫商店街的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.39,0:16:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 您也可以当我们是来维持风纪的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}柳生同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟同学人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在搞什么呢那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:16:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀 不要让旁人靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}敢小看我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.26,0:17:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}给我收拾了她们！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没办法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.16,0:17:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家没事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都这么找了也找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也许是先回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.19,0:17:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}前方禁止通行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}结束了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}切 这连准备活动都算不上嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟同学她到底出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.59,0:17:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}肯定又去哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}受到了咱家的攻击居然还能站得起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这气息！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.99,0:17:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这些家伙不是普通的不良少年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:17:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}各位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.67,0:18:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这些人都是没有心灵的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}心灵！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.22,0:18:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然动作挺迟缓的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感觉倒是挺敏锐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就像胆小的小动物一样真是可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.37,0:18:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这难道是！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍者结界！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍者结界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}此乃用于忍者间战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}超越时空的一种特殊战斗空间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就是说…这些家伙也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我们也得拿出点真本事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 来转职吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.11,0:18:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然这超出了任务之外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.36,0:18:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可也是不得已而为之
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍转身！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍转身！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍转身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是将沉睡于体内的精力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}由六门查克拉一口气释放而出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.93,0:19:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在一瞬间转化为战斗形态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍者奥义中的基本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍者通过转身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}便可以将自身所持有的能力发挥至极限
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}受你照顾了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个 还没有问你的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我叫飞鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是焰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是小焰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.66,0:19:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那再见啦 小焰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}故意放出了些杀气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}结果别说注意到…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望你的朋友能回来找你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.76,0:19:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要说我的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可爱的人偶们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.39,0:19:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为了我加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人偶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.41,0:20:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}混杂在不良少年中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用人偶来袭击咱们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过有一件事是明摆着的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被盯上的是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.76,0:20:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那些人偶 四个气息都一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像就是由同一个人操纵的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.35,0:20:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你真的是好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哇啊…好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.01,0:20:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:20:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:20:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你怎么这副样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.06,0:21:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这里面有些个中缘由…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不良少年们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.88,0:21:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}事到如今你还说什么悠闲话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}现在已经不是讲不良少年的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.92,0:21:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.38,0:21:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天飞鸟的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可得好好给雾夜老师说说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还是做好罚你坐禅的心理准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.69,0:21:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不论是哪位孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.83,0:21:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看来都能成为我美妙人偶的素材呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.92,0:21:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}结果如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.70,0:21:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那位传说中的忍者之孙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}亏我还期待她是个多么厉害的名手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.45,0:21:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}半藏学园根本就不值一惧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.79,0:21:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哼 现在暂且就让他们逍遥着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.69,0:21:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}究竟哪边才是真正的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}过不了多久她们就是不愿意也得明白
Comment: 0,0:21:54.89,0:21:55.49,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.19,0:22:16.64,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}この道で決めたから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:21.73,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}どこまでも迷わないの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.58,0:22:28.75,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}前向きな情熱に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:34.28,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}相応しい勇気が光る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:37.94,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}選んだ思いが全部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.99,0:22:41.08,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}運命だったらいいな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.18,0:22:43.27,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}覚悟はできてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.27,0:22:46.15,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}勇ましく　誇らしく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.24,0:22:49.97,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}凛々しく進もう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:52.14,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}夢に今　Ready Go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.19,0:22:55.46,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}挑んでいくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:22:59.34,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}いつだって　真っ直ぐな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.47,0:23:02.44,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}私が道しるべ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:04.86,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}毎日に　Kiss Kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:07.88,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}恋するみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.52,0:23:12.34,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}真剣勝負が基本だよね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.36,0:23:13.95,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}信じている　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.95,0:23:15.46,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}夢に秘めた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.46,0:23:20.88,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}可能性　育っている
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:23.36,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}夢に今　Ready Go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.19,0:22:16.64,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}决定要踏上这条路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:21.73,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不论走向何方也不迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.58,0:22:28.75,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}面朝前方的激情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:34.28,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}与其相符的勇气绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:37.94,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}所选所思即为全部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.99,0:22:41.08,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}即便是命运又何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.18,0:22:43.27,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我已做好了准备
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.27,0:22:46.15,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}勇敢 骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.24,0:22:49.97,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}凛凛风姿朝前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:52.14,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}梦想现在 Ready Go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.19,0:22:55.46,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}朝它挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:22:59.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不论何时 都迈步朝前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.47,0:23:02.44,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我就是路标
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:04.86,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}每天 Kiss Kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:07.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}庞若坠入爱河
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.52,0:23:12.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}真正的较量可是基本
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.36,0:23:13.95,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我所信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.95,0:23:15.46,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}是那由梦想中所隐藏的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.46,0:23:20.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}可能性 茁壮成长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:23.36,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}梦想现在 Ready Go
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葛城姐 你有什么棘手的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.95,0:23:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}果然还是胸部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.18,0:23:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.76,0:23:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为了克服这个弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.23,0:23:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来帮助我吧 飞鸟！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊…不要揉啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.55,0:23:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下回 传说之忍现身
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.47,0:23:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拼上性命来相夺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.39,0:23:39.94,Chapter,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,484)\bord2\blur2\c&HE2EEEE&\3c&H383A3B&}传说中的忍者出现
